summary: I really don’t want to sound like a downer and I definitely want everyone to have fun at their shows but please!! Be responsible...
body: I really don’t want to sound like a downer and I definitely want everyone to have fun at their shows but please!! Be responsible and aware of your surroundings if you’re drinking at your show!!! My 1989 show experience was almost ruined because the couple in front of me were trashed and kept getting up on their chairs and swinging around and spilled their wine all over me. I understand wanting to drink and let loose but pleade just be aware of the people around you (especially children). ANYWAY I LOVE YOU ALL ENJOY THIS TOUR LET’S GOOOO

summary: When she played long live I cried lol it was really frustrating because around me I was the ONLY one that knew this song ???...

When she played long live I cried lol it was really frustrating because around me I was the ONLY one that knew this song ??? Like as soon as it came on I stood up and everyone else was sat down confused and TALKED ALL THE WAY THROUGH FFS and I just sobbed lol
@taylorswift thank you for a magical evening I won’t forget. This song meant even more to me as it was the song I used to sing for my old pony who sadly passed away a couple years ago

blog.description:
The names Jacqueline. I go by Jackie or Dude because that's what Taylor Swift called me when I met her on June 1st, 2018 in Chicago, Illinois.
Taylor followed 8/15/15 and liked 1x a photo of me and my best friend just chilling and a photo of me and the love of my life on New Years day and I haven't recovered since. She also told me she saw my tour outfits and thought I was really dedicated so she saved them and had someone come find me so she could meet me!!!!!
 Feeling 23 and blessed, living in a big ol' (windy) city.
follow my insta account @ YourQueenB
Taylor Swift enthusiast since 2008. Message me, let's be friends!
